            "type": "text",
            "text": "Security and reliability"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapters trained on customer logs may memorize PII — scrub datasets before PEFT. Validate merged models do not regress on safety refusals. Treat adapter files as code artifacts: sign, scan, and restrict write access in multi-tenant deployments."
          }
        ]
      },
