            "text": "a thin adjustable overlay",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " on a frozen expert. The base model retains general language skill; adapters steer tone and format — like interchangeable lenses on the same camera body."
